{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"735a06515d","title":"对华北疫病防治情况报告的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"de5e37b8fe","index":0,"year":1952,"month":3,"day":17,"articleId":"735a06515d"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji31","name":"毛泽东全集第31卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/31-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji31":{"comments":[{"id":"40ce4ef488","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"735a06515d","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指中共中央华北局第三书记刘澜涛1952年3月15日关于华北疫病防治情况给周恩来并报毛泽东的报告。报告说，1952年入春以来，华北各地疫病相继发生，并蔓延发展，以河北、平原两省最为严重，主要是流行性感冒、麻疹、狸红热、白喉等。各级人民政府及时掌握疫情，组织力量防治，经过努力，大部地区疫病已经扑灭。但目前仍处于传柔病流行季节，各地疫病仍未彻底根除，因此，必须防止麻济思想，应继续组织力量，完全消灭现有疫病；同时发动群众，开展大规模的清洁卫生运动，进行全面预防工作，以保证人民健康和春耕抗旱工作的顺利开展。"}],"contents":[{"id":"83fdd07612","type":"title","text":"对华北疫病防治情况报告的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"735a06515d"},{"id":"40ce4ef488","type":"paragraph","text":"周总理：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"735a06515d"},{"id":"e4a940c4bf","type":"paragraph","text":"似宜通令全国各地普遍注意疫情，有疫者治疫，无疫者防疫，并将华北防治时疫文件转发各地参考，请的办。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"735a06515d"},{"id":"12ec5e95bf","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"735a06515d"},{"id":"9901cacbc9","type":"paragraph","text":"三月十七日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"735a06515d"}],"page":{"id":"2298dda182","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"735a06515d","start":514,"end":514}}}},"__N_SSG":true}